			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1127858">
									

<p>This is solid, upvoted.</p>
<p>Two things I can think of that might improve it a bit. One, what's a water charge, and why was it used? Two, it gets a bit confusing that the agents refer to one another by designation but are referenced by name. I suggest making sure it's clear in the initial documentation who's who, and the logs are formatted to show their designations rather than names so it's easier to keep straight.</p>

