														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1127881">
									

<p>Water charges are used in breaching structures. Consists of an explosive backed with water - serves to focus the blast toward the door to be opened and minimizes blast effects and shrapnel the breaching team has to deal with.</p>
<p>Will take a stab at clarifying the names/designations thing. EDIT: Thinking about it, I'm not sure it would clarify much, since the agents refer to each other by both designation, as in fire team leaders addressing their own teams and the other team leaders, and also by name when referring to individual fire team members. Will try it anyway.</p>

							</div>

								
